// ConfigClient is the client API for Config service.
//
// For semantics around ctx use and closing/ending streaming RPCs, please refer to https://pkg.go.dev/google.golang.org/grpc/?tab=doc#ClientConn.NewStream.
//
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Config — central configuration distribution (PIPELINES.md). Operators
// push a ConfigSet (trunks + upstreams + routes + pipelines + scenarios,
// shape-stable across versions) to the media-server; subscribed pods
// (sip-proxy, media-edge, ai-worker) get push notifications and swap
// their in-memory state atomically. Replaces per-pod env / YAML files
// for everything except boot bootstrap creds (WORKER_ID, MEDIA_SERVER).
